# 🛠️ OncyTech Admin Panel — UI Build Guide

> **For:** Intern Developer  
> **Project:** OncyTech Website Admin Panel  
> **Date:** March 30, 2026  
> **Backend API Base URL:** `http://localhost:8000/api` (development)

---

## 📌 What Is This?

You are building the **Admin Panel** for the OncyTech company website (oncytech.com). This admin panel will allow the OncyTech team to manage all the content on their website — blogs, team members, products, portfolio projects, customer inquiries, demo requests, job applications, and newsletter subscribers.

---

## 🧰 Recommended Tech Stack

| Layer | Recommendation |
|-------|---------------|
| Framework | **Vite + React** |
| Styling | **Tailwind CSS** |
| Icons | **Lucide React** |
| HTTP Client | **Axios** or **fetch** |
| State Management | React Context or **Zustand** |
| Date Formatting | **date-fns** or **dayjs** |
| Rich Text Editor | **TipTap** or **React Quill** (for blog content) |
| File Uploads | Standard `<input type="file">` with `FormData` |
| Notifications/Toasts | **React Hot Toast** or **Sonner** |
| Tables | Custom-built or **TanStack Table** |

---

