### PAGE 2: Inquiries (`/inquiries`)

**Purpose:** View and manage all inquiries submitted from the website (IdeaPopup, Contact Form).

#### Top Section
- Page title: "Inquiries"
- Filter tabs: `All` | `New` | `In Progress` | `Completed` | `Rejected`
- Search bar (search by name or email)

#### Main Table

| Column | Type | Sortable |
|--------|------|----------|
| # | Auto-increment row number | No |
| Name | Text | Yes |
| Email | Text (clickable, opens mailto) | Yes |
| Phone | Text | No |
| Budget | Text | No |
| Source | Badge (e.g., "Landing Page", "Contact Form") | No |
| Status | Colored Badge | No |
| Date | Formatted date | Yes |
| Actions | Dropdown: View, Edit Status, Delete | — |

#### Click "View" → Inquiry Detail Modal/Drawer

**Shows all fields:**
- Name, Email, Phone, Budget
- Project Brief (full text, multi-line)
- Source, IP Address, User Agent
- Status (with dropdown to change)
- Admin Notes (editable textarea)
- Created date, Updated date
- "Save Changes" button (updates status + admin notes)
- "Delete" button (with confirmation dialog)

**API Calls:**
```
GET    /api/inquiries                    ← List all (with ?status=NEW filter)
GET    /api/inquiries/:id               ← Get single inquiry
PATCH  /api/inquiries/:id               ← Update status/notes
DELETE /api/inquiries/:id               ← Delete inquiry
```

**Pagination:** Bottom of table — Page numbers, Previous/Next buttons, "Showing 1-10 of 47"

