### PAGE 3: Blog Management (`/blogs`)

**Purpose:** Create, edit, publish, and delete blog posts that appear on the Insights page.

#### Blog List View (`/blogs`)

**Top Section:**
- Page title: "Blog Posts"
- "New Blog Post" button (top-right, blue gradient)
- Filter tabs: `All` | `Published` | `Drafts`
- Search bar

**Table/Card Layout:**

| Column | Type |
|--------|------|
| Cover Image | Thumbnail (60x60) |
| Title | Text (bold, clickable → edit page) |
| Category | Badge |
| Author | Text |
| Status | Badge: Published (green) / Draft (gray) |
| Date | Formatted createdAt |
| Actions | Edit, Toggle Publish, Delete |

#### Create/Edit Blog (`/blogs/new` or `/blogs/[id]/edit`)

**Full-page form with two columns on desktop:**

**Left Column (Main Content - 70% width):**
- **Title** — Large text input
- **Slug** — Auto-generated from title, but editable (e.g., "my-blog-post")
- **Content** — Rich text editor (TipTap or React Quill)
  - Should support: Bold, Italic, Headings, Lists, Links, Images, Code blocks
- **Excerpt** — Textarea (short summary, 2-3 lines)

**Right Column (Sidebar - 30% width):**
- **Status Card:**
  - Toggle: Published / Draft
  - "Save as Draft" button
  - "Publish" button (blue gradient)
- **Cover Image:**
  - Image preview area
  - "Upload Image" button
  - "Remove" link
- **Category:**
  - Dropdown: "AI & Machine Learning", "Web Development", "Mobile Development", "Blockchain", "UI/UX Design", "Technology Trends", "Cloud Engineering"
- **Tags:**
  - Multi-input (type a tag, press Enter to add, click X to remove)
  - Shows tags as small badges

**API Calls:**
```
GET    /api/blogs                 ← List all blogs (admin gets all including drafts)
GET    /api/blogs/:id             ← Get single blog for editing
POST   /api/blogs                 ← Create new blog
PATCH  /api/blogs/:id             ← Update blog
DELETE /api/blogs/:id             ← Delete blog
POST   /api/upload/image          ← Upload cover image (NEW API needed)
```

