## 🎨 Design Guidelines

### Color Palette

| Usage | Color | Hex |
|-------|-------|-----|
| Primary / Buttons | Blue Gradient | `from-[#34C5F3] via-[#329DF6] to-[#224DBB]` |
| Sidebar Background | Dark Navy | `#0f172a` |
| Sidebar Active Link | Lighter Navy | `#1e293b` |
| Sidebar Text | Light Gray | `#94a3b8` |
| Sidebar Active Text | White | `#ffffff` |
| Page Background | Light Gray | `#f8fafc` |
| Card Background | White | `#ffffff` |
| Text Primary | Dark | `#0f172a` |
| Text Secondary | Gray | `#64748b` |
| Success / Active | Green | `#22c55e` |
| Warning / In Progress | Yellow | `#f59e0b` |
| Danger / Rejected | Red | `#ef4444` |
| Info / New | Blue | `#3b82f6` |

### Status Badge Colors

| Status | Background | Text |
|--------|------------|------|
| NEW | `#dbeafe` | `#1d4ed8` |
| PENDING | `#dbeafe` | `#1d4ed8` |
| IN_PROGRESS | `#fef3c7` | `#92400e` |
| REVIEWING | `#fef3c7` | `#92400e` |
| CONFIRMED | `#d1fae5` | `#065f46` |
| COMPLETED | `#d1fae5` | `#065f46` |
| PUBLISHED | `#d1fae5` | `#065f46` |
| HIRED | `#d1fae5` | `#065f46` |
| REJECTED | `#fee2e2` | `#991b1b` |
| CANCELLED | `#fee2e2` | `#991b1b` |
| DRAFT | `#f1f5f9` | `#475569` |
| INACTIVE | `#f1f5f9` | `#475569` |

### Component Patterns

**Tables:**
- Zebra striping (alternate row background)
- Hover highlight on rows
- Sticky header
- Loading skeleton while data is fetching
- Empty state with illustration when no data

**Forms:**
- Label above each field
- Red asterisk (*) for required fields
- Inline validation errors below fields
- Disabled submit button while loading
- Success toast notification on save

**Modals:**
- Centered overlay with backdrop blur
- Close button (X) top-right
- "Cancel" + "Confirm" buttons at bottom

**Confirm Dialogs (for Delete actions):**
- "Are you sure?" title
- Description of what will happen 
- "Cancel" (gray) + "Delete" (red) buttons
- Must type something or click checkbox to confirm (for important deletes)

