## ✅ Build Order (Recommended)

Build in this order so you can test each module independently:

| Phase | Pages | Priority |
|-------|-------|----------|
| 1 | Login page + Auth guard + Sidebar layout | 🔴 Must do first |
| 2 | Dashboard (stats cards + recent tables) | 🔴 High |
| 3 | Inquiries (list + detail + status update) | 🔴 High |
| 4 | Blogs (list + create/edit with rich text editor) | 🔴 High |
| 5 | Employees (list + create/edit + reorder) | 🟡 Medium |
| 6 | Products (list + create/edit) | 🟡 Medium |
| 7 | Portfolio (list + create/edit) | 🟡 Medium |
| 8 | Demo Requests (list + detail) | 🟡 Medium |
| 9 | Job Applications (list + detail) | 🟢 Lower |
| 10 | Newsletter (list + export) | 🟢 Lower |
| 11 | Settings (profile + change password) | 🟢 Lower |

---

> [!TIP]
> **Start with the Sidebar + Layout first.** Once that shell is working, every new page is just adding a new component inside the same layout.
